idth: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3835879" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/OasisStandingOnTheShoulderOfGiants-25th-anniversary-reissue.jpg" alt="利亚姆·加拉格尔（Liam Gallagher）在2000年与绿洲现场表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/OasisStandingOnTheShoulderOfGiants-25th-anniversary-reissue.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/OasisStandingOnTheShoulderOfGiants-25th-anniversary-reissue-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/OasisStandingOnTheShoulderOfGiants-25th-anniversary-reissue-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/OasisStandingOnTheShoulderOfGiants-25th-anniversary-reissue-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/OasisStandingOnTheShoulderOfGiants-25th-anniversary-reissue-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/OasisStandingOnTheShoulderOfGiants-25th-anniversary-reissue-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3835879" class="wp-caption-text">利亚姆·加拉格尔（Liam Gallagher）于2000年与绿洲现场表演。信贷：贝特兰·吉（Bertrand Guay）/法新社/盖蒂（Getty）</figcaption></figure><p> Oasis将于今年开始进行大规模的复出巡回演出，这是他们自2009年以来的第一场现场表演。备受期待的跋涉将于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-tour-uk-ireland-stadium-2025-liam-noel-gallagher-tickets-3787539">今年夏天在英国和爱尔兰举行的一场体育场演出</a>开始，随后是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-add-extra-dates-to-north-american-2025-reunion-tour-due-to-phenomenal-demand-3799159">一系列的日期北美</a>。</p><p>然后，该小组将在9月下旬<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-wembley-stadium-extra-reunion-dates-tickets-invite-only-no-surge-pricing-3790552">在伦敦的温布利体育场举行两次额外演出</a>，然后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-south-korean-and-japan-dates-for-their-2025-reunion-tour-3814881">前往韩国和日本</a>。在今年11月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-2025-south-american-reunion-tour-dates-the-brothers-are-coming-buy-tickets-3809661">在南美举行的广泛巡回演出</a>之前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-add-more-dates-to-australia-2025-reunion-tour-3801693">，澳大利亚举行了更多音乐会</a>。</p><p>在其他利亚姆·加拉格尔（Liam Gallagher）新闻中，这位音乐家最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-responds-thousands-oasis-tickets-cancelled-speaks-out-on-special-guests-3836620">在绿洲聚会的数千张门票被Ticketmaster取消后发表了回应</a>。</p><p>然而，尽管为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-partner-with-twickets-for-reunion-tour-3788427">防止吹捧以夸张的价格重新销售其吹捧的努力</a>，但英国节目的门票仍在八月发售，但大约有50,000张门票在转售地点最终出现。作为回应，发起人Live Nation和SJM确认， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-are-preparing-to-cancel-more-than-50000-tickets-sold-via-secondary-ticket-sites-3807274">通过二级售票网站出售的所有门票将被取消</a>，并通过Ticketmaster以面值再次提供。 </p><figure id="attachment_3800092" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3800092" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3800092" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/OasisAustralian-tour-dates-announcement.jpg" alt="绿洲的利亚姆和诺埃尔·加拉格尔" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/OasisAustralian-tour-dates-announcement.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/OasisAustralian-tour-dates-announcement-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/OasisAustralian-tour-dates-announcement-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/OasisAustralian-tour-dates-announcement-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/OasisAustralian-tour-dates-announcement-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/OasisAustralian-tour-dates-announcement-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3800092" class="wp-caption-text"> Oasis的Liam和Noel Gallagher。学分：西蒙·埃米特（Simon Emmett）</figcaption></figure><p>但是，这一过程远非如此， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/thousands-of-oasis-tickets-are-now-being-cancelled-by-ticketmaster-in-bot-crackdown-but-many-fans-are-unhappy-3836142">周末有许多粉丝在社交媒体上访问社交媒体，声称他们在合法地购买了他们的门票后被错误取消了。</a></p><p>他本周早些时候上了X/Twitter <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-responds-thousands-oasis-tickets-cancelled-speaks-out-on-special-guests-3836620">，回应了一个伸出援手问的球迷</a>：“利亚姆，您如何看待门票情况？认为粉丝是机器人，并返回了钱吗？”在回应时，英国人偶像写道：“我不制定规则。我们正在尝试做正确的事情。就是这样，我是歌手。离开我的案子。”</p><p>最近，该乐队被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-new-order-the-white-stripes-mariah-carey-lead-nominations-for-rock-and-roll-hall-of-fame-2025-3837368">提名为今年的摇滚名人堂</a>。在提名提名之后，利亚姆·加拉格尔（Liam Gallagher） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-says-rock-and-roll-hall-of-fame-is-for-wankers-after-oasis-nominated-3837513">猛烈抨击了点头</a>：“ RNR名人堂是为wankers for Wankers”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-are-re-releasing-all-standing-on-the-shoulder-of-giants-music-videos-in-4k-3837541">绿洲后重新发行了所有“站在巨人队的音乐视频的肩膀上，第4K</a>的肩膀都出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
